Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:04.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all\nthe shards of the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:08.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku with my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:13.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koga is seriously hurt during his\ndesperate battle with the Band of Seven.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:16.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Furthermore, the power of\nthe sacred barrier around Mt. Hakurei{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}has the power to even\nhinder Sesshomaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:20.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's up to us and Miroku,\NSango, Shippo and Kirara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:22.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Travel back in time for\na Feudal Fairy Tale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:24.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:15.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:22.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga is hurt! Can't you be more\ngentle with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:24.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be gentle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:28.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By rights, I should take\nthe Sacred Jewel shards from his legs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:30.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and leave him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:35.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah?\NSo why didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like I would take advantage of\na guy who can't defend himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:15.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?\NWhy can't I move?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}These damned kids...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Sesshomaru's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care of the kids later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We need to lure Sesshomaru\ninto the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0} Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've found them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're just beyond this point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:50.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}P- Please wait, Lord Sesshomaru!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:06.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're using Rin as bait to\nlure you into the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you proceed any {\i1}further....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:10.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:12.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't Lord Sesshomaru\nfeel anything?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:17.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I the only one\nfeeling weak?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:21.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, I must be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I really set my mind to it,\NI can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't do a {\i1}thing....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did Suikotsu do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:04.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu had the same\nkind face as before, {\i1}but....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:07.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,inside, {\i1}he's....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:17.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mt. Hakurei has no effect\non Suikotsu anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:22.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sacred Jewel shard has become\nmore tainted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Sesshomaru isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess the barrier is too strong\nfor him to come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't seem that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:40.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You anticipated our moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a demon, yet the barrier's\nnot affecting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:02.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His moves are dulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must leave this village,\nchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But where will we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:16.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you linger any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,other misfortunes may\nbefall you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:31.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}dead beings like us all end up\nwith the same fate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:34.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So let's both live as long\nas we can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't care about the other world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:43.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna do as I please\nwhile I live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:53.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've been on this road before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps we're lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:06.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The faster we turn around,\nthe easier it'll be to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:12.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This cave is quite deep and complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me you don't\nknow the way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:22.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All I did was follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There you go again!\NBlaming others!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:41.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You saw that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:45.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems to be luring us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:55.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It may be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't sense any demonic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:02.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh {\i1}well....{\i0} Nothing ventured,\nnothing gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:09.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let those two go\nany further.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please... follow me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boy, you're so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can barely stand, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because of the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:43.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bastard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Acting like he's perfectly fine,\nwhen he's not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:51.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's steadily trying to move\naway from the barrier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must be hard on him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:09:00.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu, don't move away\nfrom the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't need to be\ntold that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:05.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and take care\nof that bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:10.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm just itching to kill this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:17.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I couldn't kill those village kids\nbecause that doctor interfered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time I'll do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:23.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:31.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Make one wrong move\nand this kid is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:41.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although, it's all a matter\nof time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:45.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Matter of time, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!\NWhat's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Should you be\nlaughing like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He threw his sword away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:38.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Up close, you sure are good-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you've made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:45.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't be killed like a normal man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:52.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jakotsu, can I kill her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could be because I've been injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but the bastard doctor is too\nscared to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:03.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right now, this urge to kill\nis overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:09.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:26.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suikotsu, the light from your Sacred Jewel\nshard is tainted black.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're no longer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}woman....{\i0}\NShe scares me the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady {\i1}K-Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:23.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was finally able to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:32.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A dark light interfered\nand I couldn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:37.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did my sacred arrow\npurify the shard?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I to do with him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:46.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must I kill him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:59.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,please remove the shard\nfrom my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:05.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I will return to bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:11.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... wish to be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You would choose death?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:22.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I finally {\i1}remember....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I died once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:40.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure,\nlmpure is pure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:44.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,While I lived, I was confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:50.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About what was right\nand what was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:54.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll save her!\NI promise to save her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor, she's beyond help.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's just leave her\nand run!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't be ridiculous!\NThere's hope still!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The samurai will come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:06.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We must flee or they'll kill us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then run.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to save...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why you...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:21.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:24.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I put her out of her misery.\NYou should be grateful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our lord's orders...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:34.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}to kill every single person\nin this village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:42.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And {\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:04.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I who was sworn to save\npeople's {\i1}lives....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:10.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,killed someone with\nmy own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looking {\i1}back....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was unable to forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:35.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was then....that I heard the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:40.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why don't you quit\nthe good-guy act?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:45.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real you isn't interested\nin helping people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deep inside, you want to kill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're itching to kill\nand kill and kill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I finally {\i1}realized....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:01.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that the one speaking\nwas myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:07.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm finally free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill anyone who\ngets in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:19.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A totally different evil\nlurked in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:27.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that evil made me\nkill again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not long afterward, I met\NBankotsu and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:45.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,joined the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:49.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And killing felt like such a\nnatural thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:59.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The other me has killed\nso many, many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:05.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the doctor in me was\nhelpless to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how many lives\NI {\i1}saved....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how I tried\nto make a {\i1}difference....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:15.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,my soul cannot be redeemed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. {\i1}Suikotsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:24.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good and evil coexist in\nall men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must not give in to\nthe evil in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Lady {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:35.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I would probably do\nexactly the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:41.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I cannot endure that thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please, Lady {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:52.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,remove the shard\nand release my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please Lady {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:11.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dead beings like us all end up\nwith the same fate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take it as a memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:41.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is as it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:10.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suikotsu, may you find peace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:14.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm.... Priestess....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must've been scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this {\i1}person....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:27.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:33.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:41.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must leave this place, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before the souls within me fade\nand I cannot move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The priestess who\nput Inuyasha under seal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She is just like those others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The undead... reeking with the smell\nof bone and grave dirt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she get a glimpse\nof her own fate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:05.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:08.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want them to return.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:32.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must not let them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:52.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess we were walking\naround all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:56.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did that apparition\nmake us do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This....!{\i0}\NThis can't {\i1}be....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A cape made from\nglowing moss.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Demon Slayer uses it\nfor night raids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku was here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:26.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koga....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:28.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:30.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't die, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's Inuyasha thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:50.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Beautiful {\i1}weather....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.39,0:23:48.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To avenge Ginkotsu's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:50.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Renkotsu has his eyes\non Koga's Sacred Jewel shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:52.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The river is covered with oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:54.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's nowhere for you to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:56.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He has exploding bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:57.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's gonna blow up this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:23:59.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't live either!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.34,0:24:02.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will not die!\NOnly you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:05.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if I'd let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:09.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Vanished in a River of Flames"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.65,0:24:11.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did the mutt get blown to bits?!
